                <h1>Explore the Freedom of Modern Dance: Movement That Inspires</h1>
                <p>Modern dance is a dynamic art form that breaks free from traditional ballet constraints. It embraces individual expression, rhythm, and movement innovations, allowing dancers to explore their feelings through body language. With roots in early 20th century rebellion, modern dance continues to evolve, blending various styles and techniques.</p>
